freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Armpit lymph node swelling persists in the arm that I received the vaccination in. Swelling ebbs and flows in size ranging from quarter size to over golfball sized. At 68 hrs post vaccine, the opposite armpit also has some mild swelling.

Large swollen lymph node in my left armpit about the size of a half dollar that started last night, was larger this morning and now is a little smaller, about quarter sized, but quite sore with out being touched and tender to touch as well..
Metallic blood taste in my mourh for an hour
Strange pulsating/mild tingling in 4th and 5th digits of bilateral hands starting at 17 hrs post vaccine.
